Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.83,0:57:02.64,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.24,0:57:09.04,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,好好地舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.64,0:57:11.64,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.85,0:57:16.25,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,那就插入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.66,0:57:29.86,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,初川先生 我是送快遞的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.27,0:57:43.08,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,初川先生
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.68,0:57:47.88,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,初川先生
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.08,0:57:53.49,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,妳不要做奇怪的事\N不然會被懷疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.09,0:57:59.29,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,初川先生
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.30,0:58:08.90,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.32,0:58:32.73,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.53,0:58:37.93,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我看了一款摩托車 這個如何
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.73,0:58:44.54,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不知道選哪個顏色好\N小南覺得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.74,0:58:45.54,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.74,0:58:50.54,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,什麼為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.94,0:58:52.55,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,有孩子的話有車比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.75,0:58:55.35,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我們才剛買了房子
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.55,0:58:56.95,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,還有房貸沒還
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.55,0:58:59.15,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,你怎麼還有錢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.15,0:59:02.76,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,因為我很努力工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.76,0:59:06.16,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,得到了很多獎金
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.56,0:59:09.16,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,小南妳好奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.16,0:59:11.36,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.36,0:59:13.97,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我身體不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.77,0:59:16.57,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,小南
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.38,0:59:26.18,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,（5月27日）
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.18,0:59:33.39,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,你們吵架了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.19,0:59:39.39,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,竟然想買車
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.99,0:59:42.39,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,越來越可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.00,0:59:44.00,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.81,0:59:58.01,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.21,1:00:00.81,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,老公的業績很高
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.21,1:00:05.02,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,應該沒有貪污吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.23,1:00:20.23,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.63,1:00:23.44,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,妳認為我在說謊嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.44,1:00:32.85,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我是為了誰每天努力隱瞞呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.25,1:00:40.85,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,妳還這麼說的話\N我就不管了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.46,1:00:45.66,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.06,1:00:50.86,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.67,1:00:54.47,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.87,1:00:59.87,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,只要妳協助我就行
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.27,1:01:02.47,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.09,1:01:22.29,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.70,1:01:27.30,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,很好哦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.70,1:01:31.90,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.51,1:01:39.11,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,（5月28曰）
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.34,1:02:07.14,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.94,1:02:08.74,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,小南
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.54,1:02:12.95,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,部長說今晚有話要聊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.75,1:02:15.35,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我很晩才回來
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.55,1:02:19.35,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.15,1:02:22.76,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,昨天很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.36,1:02:25.56,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我應該早點和妳商量
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.76,1:02:27.76,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,但是我也好好考慮了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.76,1:02:30.96,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,錢的事情沒問題
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.57,1:02:35.37,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.17,1:02:38.97,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不會很晚的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.57,1:02:40.77,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,再聯繫吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.38,1:02:44.18,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.38,1:02:46.58,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.05,1:04:00.85,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.45,1:04:04.46,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,小南 睡覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.46,1:04:09.26,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,小南
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.47,1:04:16.67,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,小南
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.67,1:04:17.47,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.87,1:04:19.07,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,還沒睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.87,1:04:21.27,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,對了 部長
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.08,1:04:24.08,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,這是小南
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.08,1:04:26.48,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,抱歉這麼晚打擾了 太太
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.88,1:04:32.68,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.69,1:04:34.69,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.49,1:04:36.29,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.69,1:04:37.89,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,請進
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.09,1:04:40.49,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,抱歉 家裡很髒
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.49,1:04:43.50,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,小南
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.70,1:04:45.70,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,拿啤酒來
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.10,1:04:52.10,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,請坐吧\N好的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.91,1:04:55.91,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 喝太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.91,1:04:59.51,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,小南
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.91,1:05:03.12,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,啤酒呢 小南
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.32,1:05:04.52,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,在這裡呀
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.92,1:05:07.12,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,拿點小吃來
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.72,1:05:10.52,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.32,1:05:13.13,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,漢堡排吃完了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.73,1:05:15.13,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,真的很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.33,1:05:16.33,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.93,1:05:23.74,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,有這麼漂亮的太太 做菜又好吃\N你真幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.74,1:05:26.54,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,都是多虧了部長
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.14,1:05:31.74,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我有部長這樣的上司真幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.54,1:05:33.35,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.95,1:05:41.55,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,能幹的人什麼事情都能做好
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.96,1:05:48.36,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我知道部長很照顧我
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.16,1:05:51.16,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.56,1:05:54.57,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我一輩子都會跟著部長
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.97,1:05:56.97,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.37,1:05:59.57,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,沒事吧\N沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.37,1:06:02.37,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,喝點水比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.57,1:06:03.38,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.18,1:06:07.78,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,那個居酒屋真的不錯昵
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.38,1:06:09.78,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,你經常去嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.18,1:06:11.18,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.38,1:06:13.99,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.39,1:06:15.79,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,非常好喝
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.39,1:06:19.79,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,那裡的料理也很好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.59,1:06:23.40,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,小南
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.60,1:06:24.60,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,啤酒還沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.20,1:06:27.60,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.80,1:06:30.00,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,太太也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.20,1:06:32.40,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,太太 我來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.01,1:06:34.81,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不必了\N沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.82,1:06:49.62,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.42,1:06:52.02,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不關我的事
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.23,1:06:54.43,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,是他邀請我的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.43,1:06:58.43,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.43,1:07:01.03,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,妳說昵
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.84,1:07:09.64,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.05,1:07:22.25,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.86,1:07:27.26,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,會被老公聽到的
