Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.58,1:49:30.98,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.38,1:49:36.39,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.99,1:49:43.79,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.61,1:50:04.61,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,變得好濕哦
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.03,1:50:17.03,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.43,1:50:26.24,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.24,1:50:28.44,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.47,1:51:05.47,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.10,1:51:36.71,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.11,1:51:43.71,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,繼續插吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:22.15,1:52:22.95,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.97,1:52:41.37,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,高潮了幾次呢
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.17,1:52:43.97,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,自己摸摸看吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.78,1:52:46.78,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.38,1:52:49.18,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.19,1:52:58.99,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.59,1:53:03.19,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,射在小穴裡哦
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.40,1:53:14.80,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:53:15.60,1:53:16.61,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.81,1:53:17.81,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.62,1:53:33.82,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,射出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.67,1:54:25.47,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,1:55:09.32,1:55:12.12,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,（6月10曰）
Dialogue: 0,1:55:12.12,1:55:12.92,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:14.72,1:55:15.52,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.13,1:55:20.93,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,好累呀
Dialogue: 0,1:55:23.93,1:55:27.34,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,安倍私吞公款了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.94,1:55:32.74,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:34.74,1:55:35.95,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.95,1:55:40.15,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,他似乎和太太離婚了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.95,1:55:43.35,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,也許他因為醫藥費 很需要錢
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.76,1:55:48.76,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,安倍怎麼了昵
Dialogue: 0,1:55:50.36,1:55:51.76,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,他也知道的
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.76,1:55:56.17,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,他突然間無故缺勤\N找不到人了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.57,1:56:02.97,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,郵箱裡有一封信件
Dialogue: 0,1:56:07.98,1:56:09.78,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,沒有寫是誰寄的
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.58,1:56:11.38,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,是什麼昵
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.98,1:56:15.18,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,似乎是DVD
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.38,1:56:16.59,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,妳知道是什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.79,1:56:25.79,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.21,1:56:43.81,Jorcy,,0,0,0,,(初川南）
